        <updateDate>2020-06-04T15:26:33Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Rural Transportation Improvement Act </b></p> <p>This bill authorizes funding through FY2025 from the Mass Transit Account of the Highway Trust Fund to provide formula grants for rural areas.</p> <p>Additionally, the bill increases the percentage of funds available from 2% to 3% for the Department of Transportation to provide grants and contracts for transportation research, technical assistance, training, and related support services in rural areas.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
